<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="light" lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8"/>
  <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
  <title>설성클라우드 - IT 솔루션 & 서비스</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms,container-queries"></script>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <script id="tailwind-config">
    tailwind.config = {
      darkMode: "class",
      theme: {
        extend: {
          colors: {
            "primary": "#136dec",
            "background-light": "#f6f7f8",
            "background-dark": "#101822",
          },
          fontFamily: { "display": ["Inter", "sans-serif"] },
          borderRadius: {
            "DEFAULT": "0.25rem", "lg": "0.5rem",
            "xl": "0.75rem", "full": "9999px"
          },
        },
      },
    }
  </script>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; min-height: max(884px, 100dvh); }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    section[id] { scroll-margin-top: 64px; }
    .no-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
    .no-scrollbar { -ms-overflow-style: none; scrollbar-width: none; }
    /* PC: taller scroll offset for fixed header */
    @media (min-width: 1024px) {
      section[id] { scroll-margin-top: 72px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 font-display min-h-screen flex flex-col">

  <!-- ════════════════════════════════
       HEADER
       Mobile: logo + dark toggle
       Desktop: logo + nav links + dark toggle
  ════════════════════════════════ -->
  <header class="sticky top-0 z-50 bg-background-light/80 dark:bg-background-dark/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-primary/10">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-4 max-w-md mx-auto lg:max-w-7xl">

      <!-- Logo -->
      <a href="#home" class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-shrink-0">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-primary rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white" style="font-size:20px">cloud</span>
        </div>
        <span class="font-bold text-xl tracking-tight">설성클라우드</span>
      </a>

      <!-- Desktop Nav (hidden on mobile) -->
      <nav class="hidden lg:flex items-center gap-8">
        <a href="#home"     data-section="home"     class="nav-link text-sm font-semibold text-primary transition-colors hover:text-primary/70">홈</a>
        <a href="#services" data-section="services"  class="nav-link text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 transition-colors hover:text-primary">서비스</a>
        <a href="#about"    data-section="about"     class="nav-link text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 transition-colors hover:text-primary">회사소개</a>
        <a href="#contact"  data-section="contact"   class="nav-link text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 transition-colors hover:text-primary">문의</a>
      </nav>

      <!-- Right actions -->
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <!-- Desktop CTA button -->
        <button onclick="scrollTo('contact')" class="hidden lg:flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 bg-primary text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-xl hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors">
          상담 신청하기
        </button>
        <!-- Dark mode toggle -->
        <button onclick="toggleDark()" class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary transition-colors hover:bg-primary/20">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined" id="dark-icon">dark_mode</span>
        </button>
      </div>

    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="flex-1">

    <!-- ════════════════════════════════
         HOME SECTION
         Mobile: stacked (text → image → stats)
         Desktop: left text + right image, stats full-width below
    ════════════════════════════════ -->
    <section id="home">

      <!-- Hero wrapper -->
      <div class="max-w-md mx-auto lg:max-w-7xl lg:px-8">

        <!-- Desktop: grid 2-col | Mobile: stacked -->
        <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16 lg:items-center lg:py-20">

          <!-- Left: Text -->
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 px-6 py-12 text-center lg:text-left lg:px-0 lg:py-0">
            <div class="inline-flex self-center lg:self-start px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase">
              IT 전문 기업
            </div>
            <h1 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-4xl font-black leading-[1.1] tracking-tight lg:text-6xl">
              기술로 미래를<br><span class="text-primary">혁신합니다.</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-base font-normal leading-relaxed max-w-sm mx-auto lg:mx-0 lg:text-lg lg:max-w-md">
              클라우드 인프라, 맞춤형 소프트웨어, 사이버 보안으로 기업의 디지털 전환을 이끕니다.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:justify-center lg:justify-start pt-2">
              <button onclick="scrollTo('contact')" class="flex min-w-[140px] cursor-pointer items-center justify-center rounded-xl h-12 px-6 bg-primary text-white text-base font-semibold shadow-lg shadow-primary/20 hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors">
                상담 신청하기
              </button>
              <button onclick="scrollTo('services')" class="flex min-w-[140px] cursor-pointer items-center justify-center rounded-xl h-12 px-6 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-base font-semibold hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-slate-700 transition-colors">
                서비스 보기
              </button>
            </div>
            <!-- Desktop stats inline -->
            <div class="hidden lg:flex items-center gap-8 pt-4">
              <div>
                <div class="text-3xl font-black text-primary">500+</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1 font-medium">고객사</div>
              </div>
              <div class="w-px h-10 bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700"></div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-3xl font-black text-primary">14년</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1 font-medium">업력</div>
              </div>
              <div class="w-px h-10 bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700"></div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-3xl font-black text-primary">99.9%</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1 font-medium">가동률</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Right: Hero Image -->
          <div class="px-6 mb-6 lg:px-0 lg:mb-0">
            <div class="w-full h-64 lg:h-[480px] bg-center bg-no-repeat bg-cover rounded-2xl shadow-2xl shadow-primary/10"
              style='background-image: url("https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCzLNV9UHuuO1h_HsBb58rDjJ4UBO9k4QE7Tzuijz9BO6DurBm5gadlvfwmIayUGWjp-c8_tvKBN84ut9mtS-oXwhvJMhE9gKi7rK8Hx0ULcOtqNYEVQ8Bu2WE2vCkpRo04t3m-XCXjt-sr5-u09M0r1cZIWCRjkUb9IA6XJfu1_LR9jEw6f_WoQl6U27dh43NRaF42jfu0WhmX-fbamYazkOpwQROLNxmtPMNKXxSWtmNey21k-LKE4ZHLXxrJKlL4YNmY41JRCLE6");'>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>

        <!-- Mobile stats (hidden on desktop) -->
        <div class="px-6 mb-12 lg:hidden">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4">
            <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl p-5 text-center border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm">
              <div class="text-2xl font-black text-primary">500+</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1 font-medium">고객사</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl p-5 text-center border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm">
              <div class="text-2xl font-black text-primary">14년</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1 font-medium">업력</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl p-5 text-center border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm">
              <div class="text-2xl font-black text-primary">99.9%</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1 font-medium">가동률</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ════════════════════════════════
         SERVICES SECTION
         Mobile: 1→2 col grid
         Desktop: 3-col grid, wider container
    ════════════════════════════════ -->
    <section id="services" class="py-10 lg:py-20 bg-white dark:bg-slate-950/30">
      <div class="px-6 max-w-md mx-auto lg:max-w-7xl lg:px-8">

        <div class="flex items-end justify-between mb-8 lg:mb-12">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold lg:text-3xl text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">서비스</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-1">엔드-투-엔드 디지털 혁신</p>
          </div>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">arrow_forward</span>
        </div>

        <!-- 1-col mobile → 2-col sm → 3-col desktop -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 lg:gap-6">

          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 rounded-2xl border border-primary/10 bg-background-light dark:bg-slate-900 p-6 transition-all hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-primary/5 group cursor-pointer">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined">cloud</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-lg font-bold">클라우드 컴퓨팅</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm mt-2 leading-relaxed">현대 기업을 위한 확장 가능한 클라우드 인프라 솔루션.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 rounded-2xl border border-primary/10 bg-background-light dark:bg-slate-900 p-6 transition-all hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-primary/5 group cursor-pointer">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined">shield</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-lg font-bold">사이버 보안</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm mt-2 leading-relaxed">진화하는 위협에 대한 엔터프라이즈급 보안 솔루션.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 rounded-2xl border border-primary/10 bg-background-light dark:bg-slate-900 p-6 transition-all hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-primary/5 group cursor-pointer">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined">memory</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-lg font-bold">AI & 머신러닝</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm mt-2 leading-relaxed">업무 효율을 높이는 지능형 자동화 솔루션.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 rounded-2xl border border-primary/10 bg-background-light dark:bg-slate-900 p-6 transition-all hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-primary/5 group cursor-pointer">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined">all_inclusive</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-lg font-bold">DevOps</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm mt-2 leading-relaxed">팀을 위한 지속적 배포 파이프라인 최적화.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 rounded-2xl border border-primary/10 bg-background-light dark:bg-slate-900 p-6 transition-all hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-primary/5 group cursor-pointer">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined">bar_chart</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-lg font-bold">데이터 분석</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm mt-2 leading-relaxed">원시 데이터를 실행 가능한 비즈니스 인사이트로 전환.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 rounded-2xl border border-primary/10 bg-background-light dark:bg-slate-900 p-6 transition-all hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-primary/5 group cursor-pointer">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined">smartphone</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-lg font-bold">모바일 앱 개발</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm mt-2 leading-relaxed">글로벌 서비스를 위한 iOS & Android 앱 개발.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>

        <!-- CTA Banner -->
        <div class="mt-10 lg:mt-14 bg-primary rounded-3xl p-8 lg:p-12 text-center text-white relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold mb-3">IT 혁신을 시작할 준비가 되셨나요?</h2>
            <p class="text-blue-100 text-sm lg:text-base mb-6 max-w-xs mx-auto lg:max-w-sm">전문 컨설턴트와 무료 상담을 받아보세요.</p>
            <button onclick="scrollTo('contact')" class="bg-white text-primary px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-bold text-sm tracking-wide shadow-xl hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors active:scale-95">
              데모 신청하기
            </button>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full opacity-10 pointer-events-none" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 2px 2px, white 1px, transparent 0); background-size: 24px 24px;"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ════════════════════════════════
         ABOUT SECTION
         Mobile: stacked
         Desktop: mission text ↔ image side-by-side,
                  values 3-col grid, timeline ↔ team 2-col
    ════════════════════════════════ -->
    <section id="about" class="bg-white dark:bg-background-dark">

      <!-- Mission + Image -->
      <div class="max-w-md mx-auto lg:max-w-7xl lg:px-8">
        <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16 lg:items-center lg:py-20">

          <!-- Text -->
          <div class="px-6 pt-12 pb-10 lg:px-0 lg:pt-0 lg:pb-0">
            <span class="text-primary font-bold tracking-widest text-xs uppercase mb-4 block">우리의 미션</span>
            <h2 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 tracking-tight text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold leading-[1.1] mb-6">
              원활한 디지털 미래를 위한 혁신.
            </h2>
            <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-lg font-normal leading-relaxed">
              저희는 기술을 통해 사람과 기업이 잠재력을 최대한 발휘할 수 있도록 우아하고 고성능의 솔루션을 만들어 냅니다.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Image -->
          <div class="px-6 mb-12 lg:px-0 lg:mb-0">
            <div class="relative h-64 lg:h-[400px] w-full rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl shadow-primary/10">
              <img alt="디지털 네트워크" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-90"
                src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDRGL487OBxO-AZplbushj3T5KpOGilOD0N_bJ66yLaQGoc0FD3EE3vz8EPBSy4Eln_kJyLGfNv0fFWfW5ILAcUjTCrPVMgjoRfQb2aI5F8ZR81nllqlNMLqh5m01kLI9dbtqT9IR9A9SSTaS-XaBM47w0nn1CF4HoVQwR4WeE-hVJjyyNUEdwERROyrTVI94LySWMRD2FTxBaR01GEB_4rs6_rExkE5-G9zXabwWyqbyR2amMlsh9d1j953Vob1NHN0YTdNQEMFW19"/>
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/40 to-transparent"></div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Core Values -->
      <div class="mb-12 lg:mb-20">
        <div class="max-w-md mx-auto lg:max-w-7xl lg:px-8">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between px-6 lg:px-0 mb-6">
            <h3 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight">핵심 가치</h3>
            <!-- Mobile dots indicator -->
            <div class="flex gap-2 lg:hidden">
              <span class="size-2 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>
              <span class="size-2 rounded-full bg-slate-300 dark:bg-slate-700"></span>
              <span class="size-2 rounded-full bg-slate-300 dark:bg-slate-700"></span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Mobile: horizontal scroll carousel -->
        <div class="flex overflow-x-auto no-scrollbar gap-4 px-6 snap-x snap-mandatory pb-2 lg:hidden">
          <div class="min-w-[280px] flex-shrink-0 snap-start bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm">
            <div class="size-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" style="font-size:28px">verified_user</span>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-xl font-bold mb-3">신뢰</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">투명성, 정직, 책임감을 통해 고객과의 신뢰를 쌓아갑니다.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="min-w-[280px] flex-shrink-0 snap-start bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm">
            <div class="size-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" style="font-size:28px">bolt</span>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-xl font-bold mb-3">혁신</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">디지털 환경에서 가능성의 경계를 끊임없이 확장합니다.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="min-w-[280px] flex-shrink-0 snap-start bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm">
            <div class="size-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" style="font-size:28px">group</span>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-xl font-bold mb-3">협력</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">다양한 관점과 포용적인 환경을 통해 함께 성장합니다.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Desktop: 3-col grid -->
        <div class="hidden lg:grid lg:grid-cols-3 lg:gap-6 lg:px-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm">
            <div class="size-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" style="font-size:28px">verified_user</span>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-xl font-bold mb-3">신뢰</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">투명성, 정직, 책임감을 통해 고객과의 신뢰를 쌓아갑니다.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm">
            <div class="size-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" style="font-size:28px">bolt</span>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-xl font-bold mb-3">혁신</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">디지털 환경에서 가능성의 경계를 끊임없이 확장합니다.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm">
            <div class="size-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" style="font-size:28px">group</span>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-xl font-bold mb-3">협력</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">다양한 관점과 포용적인 환경을 통해 함께 성장합니다.</p>
          </div>
