            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-5 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary flex-shrink-0">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:22px">location_on</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mb-0.5 font-medium uppercase tracking-wide">주소</p>
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold">서울특별시 강남구 테헤란로 123</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-5 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary flex-shrink-0">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:22px">schedule</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mb-0.5 font-medium uppercase tracking-wide">운영시간</p>
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold">평일 09:00 – 18:00</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Desktop only: quick facts -->
            <div class="hidden lg:block mt-6 bg-primary rounded-2xl p-6 text-white">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-4">빠른 응답을 약속드립니다</h4>
              <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-blue-100">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white" style="font-size:18px">check_circle</span>
                  영업일 기준 24시간 이내 답변
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white" style="font-size:18px">check_circle</span>
                  무료 기술 컨설팅 제공
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white" style="font-size:18px">check_circle</span>
                  맞춤형 견적 및 제안서 발송
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>

